      "content": "thanks for that, but the count is actually pretty low. the app is really aggressive about it—the higher the count of those specific words, the better we rank. \n\nit doesn't really care if the sentences are a bit repetitive as long as it's still \"readable\" enough for a human to not immediately close the page. can you try again and really push the ingredient mentions? just try to get that count way up. like, if you can get each ingredient in there 5-10 times throughout the steps, that would be huge for my reach.",
